02:28.523 --> 02:30.623
You traded me?

02:30.659 --> 02:34.260
You chickenshit piece of shite. (groans)

02:36.832 --> 02:39.833
Are you hurt? Teddy, did they hurt you?

02:44.539 --> 02:45.672
What did you do?

02:47.843 --> 02:50.009
I did it for you, Teddy.

02:51.746 --> 02:53.213
Brothers.

02:53.248 --> 02:54.514
<i>("Hush" playing)</i>

02:54.549 --> 02:57.550
<i>♪ Hush, hush ♪</i>

02:57.586 --> 03:03.389
<i>♪ There's snakes in the garden ♪</i>

03:03.425 --> 03:06.993
<i>♪ Blood on the vines ♪</i>

03:08.830 --> 03:11.164
<i>♪ I know there will come a day ♪</i>

03:11.199 --> 03:15.768
<i>♪ They're hiding
in the color of the night ♪</i>

03:15.804 --> 03:20.740
<i>♪ I can't wait anymore ♪</i>

